title: Last leaves;
author: Smith, Alexander
snippet: When they cam to the fair Dodhead, They were a wellcum sight to see !

title: Last leaves;
author: Smith, Alexander
snippet: And a harried man I think I be ! There's nought left in the fair Dodhead

title: Last leaves;
author: Smith, Alexander
snippet: *' It's I, Jamie Telfer o' the fair Dodhead,
